        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"She looks like the 'Vendetta' or the 'Camorra' or some other Italian vengeance agency, doesn't she?\" said Nora with a giggle.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
