        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "Chapter fifteen",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "mr Levice, sauntering down the garden path, saw the trio approaching. For a moment he did not recognize the gentleman in his summer attire. When he did, surprise, then pleasure, then a spirit of inquietude, took possession of him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000005_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000005_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "For old man as he was, he realized that dr Kemp's strong personality was such as would prove dangerously seductive to any woman whom he cared to honor with his favor; but with a \"Get thee behind me, Satan\" desire, he had put the question from him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"This is a surprise, Doctor,\" he exclaimed cordially, opening the gate and extending his hand.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "Kemp grasped his hand heartily.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"I am a sort of surprise party,\" he answered, swinging Ethel to the ground and watching her scamper off to the hotel; \"and what is more,\" he continued, turning to him, \"I have not brought a hamper, which makes one of me.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"How is she?\" he asked, turning with him and catching a glimpse of Ruth's vanishing figure.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"Feeling quite well,\" replied Levice; \"she is all impatience now for a delirious winter season.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"I thought so,\" laughed the doctor; \"but if you take my advice, you will draw the bit slightly.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "mrs Levice was delighted to see him; she said it was like the sight of a cable car in a desert.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "He protested at such a stupendous comparison, and insisted that she make clear that the dummy was not included.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "The short afternoon glided into evening, and dr Kemp went over to the hotel and dined at the Levices' table.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "ruth, in a white wool gown, sat opposite him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "It was the first time he had dined with them; and he enjoyed a singular feeling over the situation.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "He noticed that although mrs Levice kept up an almost incessant flow of talk, she ate a hearty meal, and that ruth, who was unusually quiet, tasted scarcely anything.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "Her father also observed it, and resolved upon a course of strict surveillance.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000014_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000014_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "He was glad to hear that the doctor had to leave on the early morning's train, though, of course, he did not say so.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000014_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000014_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "As they strolled about afterward, he managed to keep his daughter with him and allowed Kemp to appropriate his wife.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "Now, when he decidedly objected to moving, it would have been heartless not to go.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"Don't consider me,\" said the doctor, observing his hesitancy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "If she had promised to take care of ruth, it would have been more to his mind; but since his wife was there, what harm could accrue that his presence would prevent?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"I should like to show my prowess to you, Miss Levice.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"In what?\" she asked, somewhat dazed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"As yet,\" corrected Kemp.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"Then will you wrap something about you and come down to the river?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "If dr Kemp wished to row, he should row; and since the Jewish mrs Grundy was not on hand, anything harmlessly enjoyable was permissible.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "ruth went indoors.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "This was certainly something she had not bargained for.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000035_000003",
