        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"Allow me,\" he said, placing his hand upon the oars.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"Indeed, no,\" she answered; \"why should I?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000046_000000",
