        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "He gently lifted her resisting fingers one by one and raised the broad bone of contention to his shoulder.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000047_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000047_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "As they approached the river, the faint susurra came to them, mingled with the sound of a guitar and some one singing in the distance.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
