        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"It looks like a cockle shell,\" he said, as he put one foot in after shoving it off.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000049_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000049_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"Will you sit in the stern or the bow, mrs Levice?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"In the bow; I dislike to see dangers before we come to them.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "He helped her carefully to her place; she thanked him laughingly for his exceptionally strong arm, and he turned to ruth.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"I was waiting for you to move from my place,\" she said in defiant mischief, standing motionless beside the boat.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000053_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000053_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"Your place?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000053_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000053_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "Ah, yes; now,\" he said, holding out his hand to her, \"will you step in?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "She took his hand and stepped in; they were both standing, and as the little bark swayed he made a movement to catch hold of her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"You had better sit down,\" he said, motioning to the rower's seat.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000057_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000057_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"I shall sit beside you and use the other oar,\" he answered nonchalantly, smiling down at her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000058_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000058_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "With a half pleased feeling of discomfiture ruth seated herself in the stern, whereupon Kemp sat in the contested throne.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000059_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000059_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"You will have to excuse my turning my back on you, mrs Levice,\" he said pleasantly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000061_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000061_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "It was a tiny boat; and seated thus, Kemp's knees were not half a foot from Ruth's white gown.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000064_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000064_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "His flannel shirt, low at the throat, showed his strong white neck rising like a column from his broad shoulders, and his dark face with the steady gray eyes looked across at her with grave sweetness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000064_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000064_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "She would have been glad enough to be able to turn from the short range of vision between them; but the stars and river afforded her good vantage ground, and on them she fixed her gaze.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000067_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000067_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "She leaned a little farther forward, looking past Kemp.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000068_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000068_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"Mamma!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000069_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000069_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "Then she straightened herself back in her seat.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000069_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000069_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "Kemp, noting the sudden flush that had rushed to and from her cheek, turned halfway to look at mrs Levice.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000069_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000069_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "Levice slept.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000070_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000070_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "dr Kemp moved quietly back to his former position.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000071_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000071_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "Against the black lace about her head her face shone like a cameo, her eyes were brown wells of starlight; she scarcely seemed to breathe, so still she sat, her slender hands loosely clasped in her lap.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
