        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "dr Kemp sat opposite her-and mrs Levice slept.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000073_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000073_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "Slowly and more slowly sped the tiny boat; long gentle strokes touched the water; and presently the oars lay idle in their locks,--they were unconsciously drifting.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000073_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000073_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "The water dipped and lapped about the sides; the tender woman's voice across the water stole to them, singing of love; their eyes met-and mrs Levice slept.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-587_54108_000075_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/587/54108/587_54108_000075_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"Doctor,\" called a startled voice, \"row out; I am right under the trees.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
