        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "\"I do not care to be Absalomed; where were your eyes, ruth?\" she complained, as Kemp pushed out with a happy, apologetic laugh.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
