        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-587",
        "content": "In five minutes Kemp had grounded the boat and helped mrs Levice out. When he turned for ruth, she had already sprung ashore and had started up the slope; for the first time the oars lay forgotten in the bottom of the boat.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
